---
import "../../../styles/home/home.css";
---

<div class="service-row reverse section">
  <div class="service-text">
    <span class="service-tag">For Growth</span>
    <h3>Technical SEO & Optimization</h3>
    <p>
      A beautiful site is useless if no one sees it. I fix the "under the hood"
      technical issues that stop Google from ranking you. I optimize speed, meta
      tags, and site structure.
    </p>
    <div class="best-for-box">
      <strong>Best for:</strong>
      <ul>
        <li>Existing sites with low traffic</li>
        <li>Slow websites</li>
        <li>Businesses targeting Google Search</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="service-image">
    <img src="/assets/Icons/wordpress-website-seo.png" alt="SEO" />
  </div>
</div>
